c: 5
v: 117
t: Hana lon peugah laen meusapeue Peue nyang Droeneuh yue nyan nyang lon peug Allah Tuhanlon ngon Tuhan gata Nyang nyan keuh saja nyang jeut taseumah Lon keuh keu saksi ateuh awaknyan Seulama mantong di lon areuwah Meunyo mantong lon sajan awaknyan Teuma ‘oh lheuh nyan pulang bak Allah Pulang bak Droeneuh meunyo mate lon Droeneuh ngieng keu lon bandum ya Allah Bandum awaknyan Droeneuh nyang jaga Dumpeue cit nyata bak Droeneuh teuhah